    <!-- Scalability -->
    <div class="jp-card jp-mt-30">
        <h3>⚡ Scalability: Multi-Server Support</h3>
        <p>Redis pub/sub enables WebSocket coordination across multiple servers:</p>

        <div class="local-panel">
            <pre class="local-panel-pre local-panel-pre-compact jp-m-0"><code>┌──────────────┐       ┌──────────────┐       ┌──────────────┐
│  Server 1    │       │  Server 2    │       │  Server 3    │
│  Client A    │       │  Client B    │       │  Client C    │
└──────┬───────┘       └──────┬───────┘       └──────┬───────┘
       │                      │                      │
       └──────────────────────┼──────────────────────┘
                              │
                    ┌─────────▼─────────┐
                    │   Redis Pub/Sub   │
                    └───────────────────┘

Client A broadcasts → Server 1 publishes to Redis → All servers receive
→ Server 2 sends to Client B, Server 3 sends to Client C</code></pre>

            <p class="jp-mt-15 jp-mb-0">
                <strong>Setup:</strong> Enable Redis in <code>app.conf</code> and the framework
